{"tid":2113081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【統戰英國】華商接觸5英揆遭起底  曾見習總三度現身閱兵","createTime":"2020-07-18T01:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T01:05:38.000Z","uid":333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"43db6298ad21b026004bdc08e461498222de71ce","tid":2113081,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T01:05:38.000Z","msg":"英國《每日郵報》日前報道，一名活躍於英國及其他國家政壇中國商人胡智榮，疑是中國潛伏在西方國家的統戰代表。報道亦提及，有英國軍情六處前情報員撰寫一個名為「中國籠絡精英計劃」（China's Elite Capture）的報告，指中國政府長期操縱英國政治和學術精英，藉此利用他們的影響力。時事評論員劉銳紹接受《蘋果》訪問時指，報道反映中國過去在海外的統戰工作失敗，沒真正做到「理念凝聚」，純粹建基於利益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他內文去蘋果睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200718/KTAEKAOF4WRHC44HAXT6AHNTXE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200718%2FKTAEKAOF4WRHC44HAXT6AHNTXE%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=f802e870\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200718%2FKTAEKAOF4WRHC44HAXT6AHNTXE%2F&h=70168b83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200718/KTAEKAOF4WRHC44HAXT6AHNTXE/</a>"}]}